cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.MA, cs.RO 

The paper proposes a novel multi-agent reinforcement learning method for traffic signal control, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The method involves deep reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the theoretical foundation and convergence to Nash Equilibrium, which relates to control systems (cs.SY) and multi-agent systems (cs.MA). Finally, the proposed method involves the decoupling of the road network, which is related to robotics (cs.RO).
